435
00:30:21,059 --> 00:30:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] Da katolici žive kako bi trebali,

436
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:25,920
[SPEAKER_00] nema zla.

437
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:27,400
[SPEAKER_00] Mlakost.

438
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:28,859
[SPEAKER_00] Mlakost je zlo.

439
00:30:28,859 --> 00:30:31,740
[SPEAKER_00] Često puta navodim taj primjer

440
00:30:31,740 --> 00:30:34,480
[SPEAKER_00] masona 33. stupnja

441
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:35,400
[SPEAKER_00] koji se obratio

442
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] na kršćanstvo.

443
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:38,339
[SPEAKER_00] I poslije novinarki govori,

444
00:30:38,339 --> 00:30:40,700
[SPEAKER_00] ona ga pita kako si gledao na crkvu

445
00:30:40,700 --> 00:30:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] kad si bio veliki meštar.

446
00:30:42,019 --> 00:30:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] I on kaže,

447
00:30:43,619 --> 00:30:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek smo ih zvali viša sila.

448
00:30:46,859 --> 00:30:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] A onda ga je pitali,

449
00:30:47,539 --> 00:30:49,319
[SPEAKER_00] pa kako ste se usudili ratovat

450
00:30:49,319 --> 00:30:50,200
[SPEAKER_00] sa višom silom?

451
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, pa mi smo znali

452
00:30:52,539 --> 00:30:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] da oni ne znaju

453
00:30:53,380 --> 00:30:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] da su viša sila.

454
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] I tako i ovu ekipu,

455
00:30:57,039 --> 00:30:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] koja je stvarno živjela

456
00:30:58,380 --> 00:31:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] jedno autentično kršćanstvo,

457
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:02,740
[SPEAKER_00] su razarali problemi iznutra.

458
00:31:02,740 --> 00:31:04,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo vidjeti koji su to problemi

459
00:31:04,759 --> 00:31:05,740
[SPEAKER_00] da ih ne ponovimo.

460
00:31:05,740 --> 00:31:07,779
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo,

461
00:31:07,779 --> 00:31:10,480
[SPEAKER_00] dogodilo se

462
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] nezdravo miješanje

463
00:31:12,940 --> 00:31:15,400
[SPEAKER_00] duhovnog i političkog.

464
00:31:16,859 --> 00:31:18,380
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno,

465
00:31:18,380 --> 00:31:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] rekao sam kako je nastalo

466
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:21,039
[SPEAKER_00] naše zajedništvo.

467
00:31:21,039 --> 00:31:23,640
[SPEAKER_00] Kad nas je bilo jako puno,

468
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] kad je primjećeno

469
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:26,740
[SPEAKER_00] da tu su i brojni studenti,

470
00:31:26,740 --> 00:31:27,720
[SPEAKER_00] intelektualci,

471
00:31:27,720 --> 00:31:29,859
[SPEAKER_00] društveno angažirani pojedinci,

472
00:31:29,859 --> 00:31:31,720
[SPEAKER_00] određene inicijative

473
00:31:31,720 --> 00:31:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] te žele pruzeći.

474
00:31:33,039 --> 00:31:34,220
[SPEAKER_00] Žele doći na gotovo

475
00:31:34,220 --> 00:31:35,700
[SPEAKER_00] i samo privući.

476
00:31:35,700 --> 00:31:37,440
[SPEAKER_00] To je bila opasnost.

477
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:40,319
[SPEAKER_00] Jednom je čak cijeli taj pokret

478
00:31:40,319 --> 00:31:42,799
[SPEAKER_00] trebao postati mladež

479
00:31:42,799 --> 00:31:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatske pučke stranke.

480
00:31:44,380 --> 00:31:46,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan Merci otišao u Palmotić

481
00:31:46,799 --> 00:31:48,279
[SPEAKER_00] i provoje cijelu noć

482
00:31:48,279 --> 00:31:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] u molitvi samo da se to

483
