[SPEAKER_00] ne dogodi u Sarajevu.

484
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:51,940
[SPEAKER_00] I pred jutro,

485
00:31:51,940 --> 00:31:53,059
[SPEAKER_00] piše u dnevniku,

486
00:31:53,059 --> 00:31:54,019
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, mislim da sam

487
00:31:54,019 --> 00:31:55,160
[SPEAKER_00] izmolio ovu milost.

