1164
00:45:51,940 --> 00:45:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kad sam nastupao

1165
00:45:53,460 --> 00:45:54,579
[SPEAKER_00] prema brojnim biskupima

1166
00:45:54,579 --> 00:45:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek sam dovio puno informacija.

1167
00:45:56,019 --> 00:45:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] On ti je zatvoren,

1168
00:45:57,000 --> 00:45:58,280
[SPEAKER_00] on neće ovo,

1169
00:45:58,420 --> 00:45:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] on je dok je bio župnik

1170
00:45:59,599 --> 00:46:00,280
[SPEAKER_00] rekao ovo.

1171
00:46:00,280 --> 00:46:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne znam je sam imao

1172
00:46:01,619 --> 00:46:03,239
[SPEAKER_00] jedno negativno iskustvo

1173
00:46:03,239 --> 00:46:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] da ti je neko rekao

1174
00:46:04,079 --> 00:46:05,179
[SPEAKER_00] ne smiješ, ne dam ti.

1175
00:46:05,179 --> 00:46:07,079
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek je imao nekad

1176
00:46:07,079 --> 00:46:08,239
[SPEAKER_00] svoje neke prohtjeve,

1177
00:46:08,239 --> 00:46:08,900
[SPEAKER_00] neko nije imao,

1178
00:46:08,900 --> 00:46:10,280
[SPEAKER_00] neko je sve blagoslivljao,

1179
00:46:10,820 --> 00:46:12,699
[SPEAKER_00] ali kad dođeš sa otvorenim srcem,

1180
00:46:12,699 --> 00:46:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] kad si autentičan,

1181
00:46:14,159 --> 00:46:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] kad si ono šta jesi,

1182
00:46:15,380 --> 00:46:18,320
[SPEAKER_00] ja nisam nigdje naišao na zatvorena vrata.

1183
00:46:18,320 --> 00:46:21,099
[SPEAKER_00] I negdje je Bog preko biskupa

1184
00:46:21,099 --> 00:46:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] odlučio da pričekamo

1185
00:46:22,380 --> 00:46:24,099
[SPEAKER_00] i sad s novim biskupima,

1186
00:46:24,099 --> 00:46:26,099
[SPEAKER_00] a novi biskupi koji su i u Hrvatskoj

1187
00:46:26,099 --> 00:46:27,179
[SPEAKER_00] i u BiH imenovani,

1188
00:46:27,179 --> 00:46:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] su i tekako dobri pastiri

1189
00:46:29,460 --> 00:46:30,239
[SPEAKER_00] i otvoreni.

1190
00:46:31,059 --> 00:46:32,400
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ćemo dobiti taj zamah

1191
00:46:32,400 --> 00:46:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] koji nam je potreban.

1192
00:46:33,420 --> 00:46:36,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1193
00:46:36,260 --> 00:46:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] Čuvajmo se zatvorenog elitizma.

1194
00:46:40,739 --> 00:46:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mi moramo biti autentični,

1195
00:46:42,960 --> 00:46:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] moramo ostati zdravi

1196
00:46:44,599 --> 00:46:47,139
[SPEAKER_00] i trebamo, kao ono, znate, stado,

1197
00:46:47,139 --> 00:46:49,400
[SPEAKER_00] najzdraviji pojedinci okruže,

1198
00:46:49,400 --> 00:46:50,800
[SPEAKER_00] najčešće muškarci,

1199
00:46:50,800 --> 00:46:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] stado i žene i djeca su onda

1200
00:46:53,579 --> 00:46:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] koji su u ranjivijoj fazi

1201
00:46:54,920 --> 00:46:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] zbog dojenja, trudne i tako,

1202
00:46:57,980 --> 00:46:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] one su u sredini.

1203
00:47:00,739 --> 00:47:01,900
[SPEAKER_00] Mi trebamo pojedince

1204
00:47:01,900 --> 00:47:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] koji će biti čvrsti,

1205
00:47:03,119 --> 00:47:04,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji će znat ko su,

1206
00:47:04,340 --> 00:47:06,659
[SPEAKER_00] ali ovi koji su najjači,

1207
00:47:06,659 --> 00:47:07,800
[SPEAKER_00] koji su na rubovima,

1208
00:47:07,800 --> 00:47:10,179
[SPEAKER_00] oni mora biti izuzetno otvoreni

1209
00:47:10,179 --> 00:47:11,860
[SPEAKER_00] dialogu prema drugima

1210
00:47:11,860 --> 00:47:13,260
[SPEAKER_00] i prema drugačijima.

1211
00:47:13,260 --> 00:47:16,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ti si iznutra potpuno siguran

1212
00:47:16,800 --> 00:47:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] ko si, ti ne moraš biti u ratu,

1213
00:47:18,619 --> 00:47:19,059
[SPEAKER_00] nisaki.

1214
00:47:19,059 --> 00:47:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ti kad si potpuno uvjeren u svoje,

1215
00:47:24,380 --> 00:47:26,079
[SPEAKER_00] ti se ne bojiš tuđeg.

1216
00:47:26,079 --> 00:47:29,659
[SPEAKER_00] I zato cilj je da sa ove

1217
00:47:29,659 --> 00:47:30,840
[SPEAKER_00] duhovne obnove

1218
00:47:30,840 --> 00:47:34,139
[SPEAKER_00] izađemo ozdravljeni,

1219
00:47:34,139 --> 00:47:35,719
[SPEAKER_00] učvršeni u svom identitetu

1220
00:47:35,719 --> 00:47:36,719
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne bojimo

1221
00:47:36,719 --> 00:47:38,179
[SPEAKER_00] dijaloga sa drugim

1222
00:47:38,179 --> 00:47:39,219
[SPEAKER_00] i drugačijim.

1223
00:47:39,219 --> 00:47:41,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ta će nastat mir.

1224
00:47:41,559 --> 00:47:43,780
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ja bavim se mirom

1225
00:47:43,780 --> 00:47:44,659
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje u Bosni i Herce.

1226
00:47:44,659 --> 00:47:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite gdje smo,

1227
00:47:45,519 --> 00:47:47,099
[SPEAKER_00] gdje imamo ovaj seminar.

1228
00:47:47,099 --> 00:47:49,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ti kad si uvjeren u svoje,

1229
00:47:49,840 --> 00:47:51,420
[SPEAKER_00] ti poštuješ drugoga.

1230
00:47:51,579 --> 00:47:55,139
[SPEAKER_00] ti ulaziš bez da poništavaš sebe,

1231
00:47:55,139 --> 00:47:57,059
