1232
00:47:57,059 --> 00:48:00,719
[SPEAKER_00] svjestan i na zdrav način ponosan na svoje,

1233
00:48:00,719 --> 00:48:02,780
[SPEAKER_00] ti ulaziš u dialog s drugim.

1234
00:48:02,780 --> 00:48:04,340
[SPEAKER_00] Takva treba biti crkva

1235
00:48:04,340 --> 00:48:07,159
[SPEAKER_00] i papa zahtijeva da takva bude karizmatska obnova.

1236
00:48:08,760 --> 00:48:11,699
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo ti koji idemo na margine.

1237
00:48:11,699 --> 00:48:14,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ti kao neizgrađen

1238
00:48:14,440 --> 00:48:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] i duhovno bolestan odeš na marginu,

1239
00:48:17,000 --> 00:48:18,780
[SPEAKER_00] nećeš ti obratiti marginu,

1240
00:48:18,780 --> 00:48:20,699
[SPEAKER_00] nego će margina tebe uništiti.

1241
00:48:20,699 --> 00:48:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] I o tome treba pričati.

1242
00:48:22,860 --> 00:48:26,139
[SPEAKER_00] Zbog toga je jako važno

1243
00:48:26,139 --> 00:48:29,360
[SPEAKER_00] da postanemo svjesni ove činjenice,

1244
00:48:29,360 --> 00:48:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] da dopustimo Bogu

1245
00:48:30,559 --> 00:48:32,440
[SPEAKER_00] da nas kroz ove dane ozdravi,

1246
00:48:32,440 --> 00:48:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi onda kao zdravi pojedinci

1247
00:48:35,159 --> 00:48:37,659
[SPEAKER_00] mogli ići na te margine

1248
00:48:37,659 --> 00:48:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] i ozdravljati.

1249
00:48:38,940 --> 00:48:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] Kako crkvu, tako i svijet.

1250
00:48:41,059 --> 00:48:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

1251
00:48:41,980 --> 00:48:55,219
[SPEAKER_00] Naučio sam se skratiti.

1252
00:48:55,219 --> 00:48:55,820
[SPEAKER_00] To je dobro.

1253
00:48:55,820 --> 00:49:06,099
[SPEAKER_00] Žena mi je u nekoj grupi na fejsu mama

1254
00:49:06,099 --> 00:49:07,699
[SPEAKER_00] i onda kaže kao pitanje

1255
00:49:07,699 --> 00:49:09,739
[SPEAKER_00] dijaspora, povratak ili ne.

1256
00:49:09,739 --> 00:49:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] I sad jedna je pošalje moj video,

1257
00:49:11,460 --> 00:49:12,780
[SPEAKER_00] onaj sjećanje i povratak.

1258
00:49:12,780 --> 00:49:14,679
[SPEAKER_00] Jovan se oduševi i kaže

1259
00:49:14,679 --> 00:49:15,699
[SPEAKER_00] na prvu sam ga vidla,

1260
00:49:15,699 --> 00:49:17,380
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam vidla sati 48,

1261
00:49:17,380 --> 00:49:19,179
[SPEAKER_00] nema šanse da bi ga pogledala.

